{"id":"amittai","term":"Amittai","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>True, the father of Jonah the prophet, a native of Gath-hepher (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 14:25\">2 Kings 14:25</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Jonah 1:1\">Jonah 1:1</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Kings 14:25","Jonah 1:1"]}